            "avatar_alignment": "top",
            "author_1": "Sarah L.",
            "text_1": "<p>The sound quality blew me away for such a compact device. I\u2019ve been using it every day for the past month and the battery still lasts all day. Fantastic build quality \u2014 feels premium in hand. Highly recommended!</p>",
            "author_2": "Marcus T.",
            "text_2": "<p>Bought this for my partner as a gift. The retro design is gorgeous and the Bluetooth pairs instantly. We ended up ordering a second one for the kitchen. Shipping was quick and packaging was excellent.</p>",
            "author_3": "Jessica R.",
            "text_3": "<p>I\u2019ve tried several portable speakers and this one stands out. Clean sound, great bass response, and it looks beautiful on my desk. Customer support was also very helpful when I had a setup question.</p>",
